{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-greetings-during-the-day/task-17","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 17","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Esteban stiže, i već je večer. Počinje razgovor pozdravom koji se koristi u ovo doba dana.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj/Slušajte zvuk i dovrši/dovršite sledeću rečenicu.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas noches</span> je pozdrav koji se koristi noću.</p>\n<p>To se prevodi kao \"večernje vesti\" ili \"dobro noć\", u zavisnosti od konteksta.</p>\n<p>U španskom, možete koristiti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas noches</span> prilikom pozdrava uveče <strong>i takođe</strong> prilikom pozdrava ili oproštaja noću. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hola, buenas noches.</span> – Zdravo, dobre večeri.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Adiós, buenas noches.</span> – Doviđenja, laku noć.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-learn-greetings-during-the-day","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-greetings-during-the-day/task-17"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Hola, BLANK.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"buenas noches","feedback":"<p>Ova fraza ima <strong>dve reči</strong> i znači \"dobro veče\" ili \"laku noć\". Koristi se kao pozdrav uveče i takođe kao način za oproštaj noću.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-boardmeeting.png","characters":[{"character":"Esteban","position":{"x":50,"y":25,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_spanish_greetings_in_the_evening.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":0.2,"finishTimestamp":1.8},"alwa